ML Gray & Silver Cufflinks$355.00

Silver cufflinks inlaid with black and gray enamel and silver Merrill Lynch logo. Completely Hand Made in Aspen Colorado from .935 tarnish resistant Italian silver. Each cufflink bears four trademarked David Bull hooves on the back inlaid with black enamel. The two toggles are set with four genuine cabochon hematite stones and each toggle is embossed with the David Bull logo. The gray and silver color combination is perfect for daytime wear. Each cufflink requires 14 steps from the initial assembly to final polish.
Packaging: Shipped in a lacquered wooden box with a special jewelry polishing cloth included.





Add to cart


SKU: ML-CL-104
Categories: Hand Made in Aspen CO, Made in the USA, Merrill Lynch Corporate Designer Gifts





